Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:19.84,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Spomínam na nádej ktorú som vídavala
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:27.66,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}kakushikirenai yuuwaku ga atta
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:27.66,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}v tvojich čistých, šťastných očiach.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:36.50,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}doushite tsumi ga aru no darou
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:36.50,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Prečo existujú hriechy?
