Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:52.87,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}To jasné svetlo na konci tunela
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:21:00.82,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}mugen ni tsuzuku yami wo sasotta
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:21:00.82,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ťa pozvalo do nekonečnej tmy.
