Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:18.27,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I ono čoskoro zmizne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:15.15,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Ahojte!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:35.10,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:38.54,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Ak rýchlo nevstanete, prídeme neskoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.64,Satoko,,0,0,0,,No tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:04.12,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Pohnite si z tých prikrývok, vy dve!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:06.51,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Takto predsa nemôžeme raňajkovať!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:08.08,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HD6026D&}Anó!
