Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:22.32,Miyo,,0,0,0,,Idem sa hrať von!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:32.04,Miyo,,0,0,0,,Pre-prepáčte mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:33.83,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Chcela by si...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:36.04,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,žiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:37.27,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Alebo zomrieť?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:39.69,Miyo,,0,0,0,,Chcem žiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:41.40,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:43.56,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Tak teda choď.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:47.02,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Aj keď tvoji priatelia nie sú doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:48.38,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Choď.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.48,0:21:51.92,Miyo,,0,0,0,,Nie sú doma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.55,0:21:54.96,Miyo,,0,0,0,,A čo keby som chcela zomrieť?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:21:59.80,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Dostala by si ďalšiu vlajočku z reštaurácie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:03.08,Miyo,,0,0,0,,To nieje fér!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:07.38,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Mama s ockom chcú ísť do obchodu bezo mňa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:09.07,Miyo,,0,0,0,,To nieje fér, to nieje fér
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:10.72,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Si si istá?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:12.62,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Určite to nebudeš ľutovať?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:16.50,Miyo,,0,0,0,,Prečo by som to mala ľutovať?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:18.57,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,To ti nepoviem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:20.69,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Nepoviem, pretože som zlá.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:26.10,Miyo,,0,0,0,,Nebojte sa, teta!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:29.83,Miyo,,0,0,0,,Nech by sa stalo čokoľvek, mama s ockom budú so mnou!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:15.76,Miyo,,0,0,0,,Už mám dvadsať vlajočiek.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.36,0:23:17.95,Miyo,,0,0,0,,Bože,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:21.06,Miyo,,0,0,0,,teraz už budem môcť byť šťastná?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.72,0:23:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.95,0:23:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezabudni si pred spaním vyčistiť zuby!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:26.92,Miyo,,0,0,0,,Dobre!
